{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"638","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"瑞典設立百萬美元獎項 尋求永續糧食解決方案","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/02/21 00:10</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社斯德哥爾摩<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>日綜合外電報導）德國與瑞典籌辦人士表示，由於氣候變遷威脅世界糧食供給，增長中的人口需要可永續糧食系統，瑞典已創立兩個<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>萬美元獎項，尋求餵飽數十億人口的解決方案。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>德國波茨坦氣候影響研究中心（<span lang='EN-US'>Potsdam Institute for Climate Change Impact Research</span>）主任羅克斯特倫（<span lang='EN-US'>Johan Rockstrom</span>）將共同主持這個獎項的評委會。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>羅克斯特倫在聲明中表示：「我們需要糧食系統革命，否則可能破壞我們星球的穩定。新的糧食星球獎（<span lang='EN-US'>Food Planet Prize</span>）旨在為此目標做出貢獻。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>瑞典科特伯格福斯基金會（<span lang='EN-US'>Curt Bergfors Foundation</span>）則指出，每年將頒發兩項糧食星球獎，第一項是獎勵「現有的可擴大永續糧食解決方案」，第二項則是獎勵「可能改變全球糧食產業的創新計畫」。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>設在斯德哥爾摩大學的斯德哥爾摩復原力中心（<span lang='EN-US'>Stockholm Resilience Center</span>）負責人高登（<span lang='EN-US'>Line Gordon</span>）指稱：「有可能在餵養<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>億人健康飲食的同時，也維持生機勃勃的生物圈。我們希望糧食星球獎能表彰可迅速擴展的最重要解決方案。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>全世界目前有<span lang='EN-US'>78</span>億人口，預計在<span lang='EN-US'>2050</span>年前成長至近<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>億。專家指出，只有改變飲食習慣、改善糧食生產和減少糧食浪費，才有可能餵飽如此規模的人口。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科特伯格福斯基金會表示，將於<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年底首次頒發這些獎項。（譯者：陳正健<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>核稿：劉學源）<span lang='EN-US'>1090220</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202002210003.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-24","clk_count":"180"}},"__N_SSG":true}